import logo from './logo.svg'; import './App.css'; function App() { return (

Troy Atkinson

Future Full-Stack Developer

  • About Me
  • Projects
  • Contact
  • LinkedIn
  • Resume

About Me

BA Communication Studies

University of Washington

class of 2018

US Navy

2008-2014

I am currently enrolled in the University of Washington's Coding Bootcamp. My plans are to find a career using my passion for design, creativity and problem solving as a developer. I am drawn to web developement by a desire to better understand the ever changing digital world we find ourselves living in daily.

Before joining Coding Bootcamp I was a staff manager and personal trainer at a gym in Seattle. before that, my studies at the Univerity of Washington focused on Journalism. And before college I had the privelage of travelling the seas and working with people from around the world while serving in the US Navy.


Interests

  • UX/UI Design
  • App Developement
  • Product Management

Skills

  • Copy Writing
  • Spanish
  • Team Management

Projects

I will be working on projects on my way to my coding certificate. Click on the project image to visit and try out my applications.


Visit my gitHub to see more!

Find My Plate

An easy to use application that allows users to find dining options in their current area or zip-code, search by cuisine, and search menus.

Your Forum

A public discussion forum where users can create groups, topics, and email invites for participants.

Weather Dashboard

A dashboard where viewers can view weather conditions and a forecast by city.

Contact Me

Seattle, Washington

troyat88@gmail.com

956-525-9865

Thanks for stopping by!


Icon Images courtesy of The Noun Project
